data.description: Large two-story home located on a corner lot. Quiet atmosphere with a covered front and back porch and beautiful Zoysia grass. Large fenced-in backyard. Game room upstairs. Updated carpet and paint throughout the home with a new gas-range stove. Wood laminate floors in the entry, study, formal dining room, and living room. Make things easier with modern home automation set up throughout the house for home lighting and thermostat which can be controlled from the convenience of your mobile device. Ecobee automated thermostats for both upstairs and downstairs allow for control from app and motion sensor enabled cooling schedules. Wemo automated switches for outdoor lights.
